==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Diffuseness
<hw>Dif*fuse"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being diffuse;
especially, in writing, the use of a great or excessive number of word
to express the meaning; copiousness; verbosity; prolixity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

